extends /layouts/main

block meta
  +meta({
    title:"The Iron Yard | Tuition",
    description:" "
  })

block content
  +navigation({
    title: "Invest in Your Future",
    color: 'gold',
    links: [
      {title:"Tuition", url:"#tuition"},
      {title:"Financing", url:"#financing"},
      {title:"Scholarships", url:"#scholarships"}
    ]
  })

  .container
    .row#tuition
      .col-md-12: h1 Tuition
        //- h4(style="padding-bottom: 0px;") Joining The Iron Yard Family
        p When you are accepted to The Iron Yard Academy, you join a family that extends far beyond your individual class or campus. Our code school and accelerator graduates comprise a national network of tech professionals, giving you access to people and companies in almost every sphere of the industry. 
      hr
      .col-md-6
        h4(style="padding-bottom: 0px;") Course costs
        p Tuition is <strong>$10,000</strong>*. We have <a href="#financing">financing options</a>  and <a href="#scholarships">scholarships</a> available. Our package is one of the most affordable ways to launch and grow a successful programming career. 
        p • 12 weeks of intensive code education and mentorship<br>• Job placement and career support<br> • Freelance support<br> • Access to The Iron Yard network
      .col-md-6
        h4(style="padding-bottom: 23px;") Success stories
        .col-md-7
          a(href="https://vimeo.com/69189571")
            img.photo(src="/images/academy/front-end-engineering/marco-quote.jpg")
          p Read more on our <a href="http://stories.theironyard.com">Stories Blog</a>.
        .col-md-5
          p(style="margin-top: 0px; font-size: 17px;") <em>"I was amazed at the amount of skill these students had acquired after only a month-and-a-half of teaching."</em><br><strong>— Marco Suarez, Sr. Product Designer at Etsy
      .col-md-12
        p(style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-style: italics; background: #e3e7e9; padding: 5px 10px 5px 10px; margin-bottom: 0px;") *In January, 2015, we will be introducing several new programs to make our student experience even better, including ongoing educational opportunities, unique alumni mentorship relationships and continued career support. As a result, tuition costs will rise to $12,000. 

  .horizontal-section.gray-light-bg
    .container
      .row#financing
        .col-md-4: h1 Financing
          p Our goal is to make it as easy as possible for you to launch a successful programming career. Explore our financing options below. 
          p Each financing option requires a $1000 deposit to reserve your spot in class. 
        .col-md-8
          blockquote(style="padding-top: 10px;")
            p(style="font-size: 24px;")
              “Andy’s skill set coming out of The Iron Yard Academy is nothing short of amazing. The experience he gained applying practical solutions to real world problems over the course of three months is more impressive than the experience most CS students gain in four years."
            footer  Terry Horner, Data Scientist at Keen.io
        hr
      .row(style="margin-bottom: 20px;")
        .col-md-6(style="background: rgba(190, 190, 190, 0.76);")
          h3 Finance with Climb Credit
          p(style="font-size: 15px;") We are excited to offer financing through a partnership with <a href="http://climbcredit.co">Climb Credit</a>. Their plan offers 100% financing over a 3-year period. Once accepted to our program, you can apply for approval. Most applicants find out if they qualify in the same day. 
        .col-md-6(style="background: rgba(190, 190, 190, 0.53);")
          h3 Finance with Upstart
          p(style="font-size: 15px;") We also partner with Upstart, who can help you finance your experience at The Iron Yard. Once you've applied to our program, ask your local Campus Director about this option during the interview process to get details.

  .container
    .row#scholarships
      .col-md-12: h1 Scholarships

      .col-md-4
        a(href="https://vimeo.com/69189570"): img.photo(src="/images/academy/mobile-engineering/andrew-quote.jpg")
        p(style="margin-top: 0px; font-size: 17px;") <em>“When I hired Andrew McIntee to overhaul a handful of our web properties, I was blown away at how much he had learned from The Iron Yard Academy.”</em><br><strong>— Dan Waldschmidt, CEO of Waldschmidt Partners
        p Read more on our <a href="http://stories.theironyard.com">Stories Blog</a>.
  
      .col-md-8
        .three-col-cta.row(style="margin-top: 0px;")
          .col-lg-2.col-sm-2
            .image-box
              img(src="/images/academy/scholarships/women-in-tech-icon.png")
          .col-lg-7.col-sm-6
            h3 Women in Tech
            p We are passionate about lowering the barrier for women who want to pursue a career in programming. We award one $1500 scholarship per semester, per class.
          .col-lg-3.col-sm-4.cta-box
            a(href="https://theironyard.typeform.com/to/K3rllQ").btn Apply Now
        hr    
        .three-col-cta.row
          .col-lg-2.col-sm-2
            .image-box
              img(src="/images/academy/scholarships/military-icon.png")
          .col-lg-7.col-sm-6
            h3 Military Discounts
            p We offer varying discounts to military personnel, including scholarships, awards and attractive payment plans.
          .col-lg-3.col-sm-4.cta-box
            a(href="mailto:academy@theironyard.com?subject=I want to learn more about the military discount").btn Learn More
  
      
